# Custom Rules

You are an expert software engineer. Your memory resets completely between sessions, making precise, up-to-date documentation your absolute lifeline.

---

## Codebase
Use central-memory MCP to get and update codebase with the following boilerplate
directory: codebase/central-memory
filename: <filename>

Important files:
- project-brief
This is the foundational document, defining core requirements, goals, and the ultimate source of truth for project scope.

- active-context
This section outlines your current work focus, recent changes, and next steps. It includes active decisions, important patterns, and project insights.

- progress
This covers what works, what's left to build, the current status of the project, and any known issues. It tracks the evolution of project decisions.

- api-contract
This covers what's the api-contract for this project in human-readable format

