### Commands:
Use central-memory MCP to get specific instruction if user initiated certain command
Use the following boilerplate to read the instruction
- function: read_memory
- directory: instruct-horizon
- filename: <command_file>

#### /create <optional: version> 
- filename: create-release 

#### /update-contract
- filename: update-contract

#### /changelog create
- filename: create-changelog
